'''2003年[[布米爾達斯省|布米爾達斯省]]地震'''是一場於2003年5月21日發生的[[矩震級|6.8 M<sub>w</sub>]]級強烈有感地震<ref name="AMER444">{{Harvnb|Oliveira|Roca|Xavier|2006|Ref=CITEREFOliveiraRocaXavier2006|p=444}}</ref><ref name="KSSE36">{{Harvnb|Keeping Schools Safe in Earthquakes|2004|Ref=CITEREF2004|p=36}}</ref>，震央位在該省一小鎮[[Thénia|Thénia]]<ref name=BBCAHE>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/world/newsid_3049000/3049101.stm Algeria hit by earthquake] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/world/newsid_3049000/3049101.stm |date=20160304063713 }} ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]''</ref><ref name="LD177">{{Harvnb|Dean|Ref=CITEREFDean|p=177}}</ref>，距離首都[[阿爾及爾|阿爾及爾]]東部約60公里<ref name=BBCAHE/>。這是阿爾及利亞[[1980年阿爾及利亞地震|20年來]]最強烈的一場地震<ref name=BBCSAESE>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/world/newsid_2936000/2936340.stm Search for Algeria earthquake survivors ends] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/cbbcnews/hi/world/newsid_2936000/2936340.stm |date=20140810022654 }} ''BBC News''</ref><ref name=BBCHDE>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/in_depth/2059330.stm History of deadly earthquakes] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/in_depth/2059330.stm |date=20110425120427 }} ''BBC News''</ref>，當時[[芮氏規模|芮氏規模]]達7.3級的強震共造成3500多人喪身<ref name=MCEER>[http://mceer.buffalo.edu/research/reconnaissance/Boumerdes5-21-03/ The Boumerdes (Algeria) Earthquake of May 21, 2003: Preliminary Reconnaissance Using Remotely Sensed Data] {{Wayback|url=http://mceer.buffalo.edu/research/reconnaissance/Boumerdes5-21-03/ |date=20080510110404 }} ''Multidisciplinary Center for Earthquake Engineering''</ref>。

政府的救災不利在災區引起廣大民怨和[[輿論|輿論]]的批評<ref name="FMENA15">{{Harvnb|Freedom House|2004|Ref=CITEREFFreedom House2004|p=15}}</ref> <ref name=BBCSAESE/>，[[2004年泛阿拉伯運動會|第十屆泛阿拉伯運動會]]也因地震而延後一年舉行。

